=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;font-family:宋体;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;2、&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;八宝-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;高原小桂林&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibviaAd9LKeIA2UdSM4vPhFen47z7eVqB1q6qH8td0lVJILaISQPhxeibqw/0&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibviaAd9LKeIA2UdSM4vPhFen47z7eVqB1q6qH8td0lVJILaISQPhxeibqw/0&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:32px;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		除了坝美，广南县的另一个景点——八宝，也美得令人窒息。八宝被誉为“高原小桂林”，有着桂林一样的喀斯特峰林地貌，温婉柔美。坐上竹筏，顺着八宝河一路慢慢飘向下游，喀斯特小山峰、万亩贡米稻田、13个壮族村落，依次排开，宛如仙境。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvgAOJNDL7RJ9zoia5gHLrphP6PoiaGeniaPxibWr6MFIwFeynsiaXEd3gAAQ/0&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvgAOJNDL7RJ9zoia5gHLrphP6PoiaGeniaPxibWr6MFIwFeynsiaXEd3gAAQ/0&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:32px;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		广南是壮族聚居区，壮族风味美食很多，比如岜夯鸡（酸汤鸡）、岜夯鱼、五色花米饭。广南由于邻近两广，饮食习惯也受到影响，所以烤乳猪也是当地的美食之一。另外，八宝所出产的八宝米在明朝时期列为贡品，不可不尝。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvPt5xX8aPK6F4VlEWDYEbvaLXvSpb2wstfOYRGXpm6jUxYDsoa5QGHw/0&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvPt5xX8aPK6F4VlEWDYEbvaLXvSpb2wstfOYRGXpm6jUxYDsoa5QGHw/0&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#548DD4;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;font-family:宋体;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;3、&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;普者黑-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;世间罕见的山水风光&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvKzj8CnTic4RHOSUnyvPAG7JGz5PvFSDGDdQFDOTvEjnqAjA3RwgBqeg/0&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvKzj8CnTic4RHOSUnyvPAG7JGz5PvFSDGDdQFDOTvEjnqAjA3RwgBqeg/0&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:32px;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		看过《爸爸去哪儿》的小伙伴一定知道普者黑，这个比泸沽湖更适合飘在水上发呆的地方。普者黑位于文山州丘北县，是一个由54个湖泊、喀斯特峰林、溶洞、少数民族村落组成的景区。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvTBRNdmeVKXX4IXtECHN9qqfibM6N3tH3HxXm7rI2ibtZEw6fz215xTjg/0&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvTBRNdmeVKXX4IXtECHN9qqfibM6N3tH3HxXm7rI2ibtZEw6fz215xTjg/0&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:32px;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		虽然不如洱海滇池般大气磅礴，但小家碧玉气质更让人迷醉。另外，这里还是全国唯一的僰人后裔聚居地，民族风情浓厚。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvAyXc033yEas0IBkOTBtF0S0oEKicheo2kSpbuZVz1HicMolYkoRhlcrQ/0&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvAyXc033yEas0IBkOTBtF0S0oEKicheo2kSpbuZVz1HicMolYkoRhlcrQ/0&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:32px;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		如何到达普者黑：在昆明东部客运站坐到丘北县的车，到达丘北县客运站后转乘景区专线公交车，半小时就能到普者黑了；另外，昆明去广南的高速公路要路过丘北县，所以也可以先玩了普者黑再去丘北县城坐车到广南，或者反过来，都行。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvZZ7ZWibtlIpUHjQENcQeVicC7ibOud8BS3BKjSJoPbb6Or4ovNoVCtz8A/0&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvZZ7ZWibtlIpUHjQENcQeVicC7ibOud8BS3BKjSJoPbb6Or4ovNoVCtz8A/0&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#548DD4;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;font-family:宋体;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;4、神秘的抚仙湖&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvzAT2cUkIgzFAX8qEGKwpAw9Ec0TtnWibZCkibLqkZGBhGNxVPFzib3bGA/0&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvzAT2cUkIgzFAX8qEGKwpAw9Ec0TtnWibZCkibLqkZGBhGNxVPFzib3bGA/0&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:32px;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		抚仙湖离昆明仅60公里，为全国第一大高原深水湖泊，天气好时水下能见度超过10米。这里是云南人的休闲度假最爱（云南人很少去三亚这些海边，对他们而言，抚仙湖足够了），飘在清澈的湖水上晒太阳，无比惬意。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvFZa5GDViaqoAUSHRCyGUIgIWdEv4TIicrsTAoSHLG4P1gkIzRWS0j3zg/0&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvFZa5GDViaqoAUSHRCyGUIgIWdEv4TIicrsTAoSHLG4P1gkIzRWS0j3zg/0&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#548DD4;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;font-family:宋体;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;5、比束河古镇更适合闲逛的地方-沙溪&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvaiczCTSg4tH2HicwJCykbBsXAmNicGYtoVcHZ9gia0sJpdib3kZPibia3Y5Nw/0&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvaiczCTSg4tH2HicwJCykbBsXAmNicGYtoVcHZ9gia0sJpdib3kZPibia3Y5Nw/0&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:32px;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		沙溪位于大理州剑川县，被联合国誉为“茶马古道上唯一幸存的集市”，如果说束河是10年前的丽江古城的话，这里就是20年前的丽江，同样的小巷流水四方街，这里却更加古朴淳厚。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvzXNRx0SIPQB8ub9XICTtAvsribZlEBFr0N3IlNAWHHObpSaVvwibmNqg/0&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvzXNRx0SIPQB8ub9XICTtAvsribZ