房”，由于整个村子都依山而建，所以，造就了“下层的屋顶就是上层的晒谷场”的奇观，被誉为“泸西布达拉宫”。本地的特色美食首推水腌菜炒肉，蜜汁牛肉、荞麦粑粑也不错。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#548DD4;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;font-family:宋体;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;10、元阳梯田-哈尼族人世代流传的杰作&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0Kdibv3BbQfqghicUdYbiaHqiaibzZKhSMICPyDMHhDTkS7Xgoey1gFw7JnNqeWg/0&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0Kdibv3BbQfqghicUdYbiaHqiaibzZKhSMICPyDMHhDTkS7Xgoey1gFw7JnNqeWg/0&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#03