:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:32px;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		如果以浓妆艳抹的少妇来形容西双版纳的话，孟连就是一位清新脱俗的傣族小卜哨。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvY8ApXo8Xcx68vbOFzEgcicKS2C8nb7atpSWcjyHZt6OEcdHau3cYqCA/0&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/J48hjRpGWnOic9hjs47X0FmPbCgd0KdibvY8ApXo8Xcx68vbOFzEgcicKS2C8nb7atpSWcjyHZt6OEcdHau3cYqCA/0&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:32px;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		位于普洱市孟连县，无论是娜允古城的傣家风情、宣抚司署的威严、集贸市场里的异国情调，还是金塔的神圣、南垒河的婀娜多姿，都是上天恩赐的无与伦比的美丽，水一般的温柔乡。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25